abstract: SEA GIRT, N.J., Sept. 4. -- New Jersey's marksmen covered themselves with glory to-day in the inter-State shooting tournament at Sea Girt. Not content with winning the regimental team match yesterday, they captured both the inter-State military and tyro company team matches to-day. abstract: OYSTER BAY, L.I., Sept. 14. -- The arrangements for the visit of the residents of Nassau County to President Roosevelt seem likely to be carried out without a hitch. abstract: The rope that suspended Marie Licastri as, one of the angels in the Italian celebration for Saint Fortunata far above a watching crowd in Elizabeth Street last night, slipped from the grasp of the man who held it on a seven-story building, and the child fell toward the street below.
